profile_positions.description:
》Gather data and run analysis to launch gambling affiliate websites;
》Improve the website UX/UI design, together with a team of designers and frontend developers;
》Ensure consistency in visual design, brand messaging and tone of voice across the website;
》Creating SEO strategy and SiteMap & define the content marketing strategy;
》Management the content writers;
》Develop and optimize all marketing and engagement tools and initiatives;
》Product owner: Take full responsibility for the product strategy, marketing outputs and results, strategies to development tasks, and learning the customers and market's requirements;
》Liaise with the affiliate manager on both the above tasks to assess impact and adaptation to the network of affiliates involved;
》Utilize in-depth analytics reports to track and improve performance.
